@startuml init_command
title Init Command

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Core" as bausteinsicht_cli_core
participant "Loader" as bausteinsicht_model_loader
participant "Engine" as bausteinsicht_sync_engine

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 1. bausteinsicht init
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 2. check if files already exist (abort with error if so)
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_model_loader : 3. Save(model.jsonc, sample specification + example elements)
bausteinsicht_cli_core -> bausteinsicht_sync_engine : 4. Run(model, document=empty, state=empty, templates, opts)
bausteinsicht_sync_engine --> bausteinsicht_cli_core : 5. initial arch.drawio written
bausteinsicht_cli_core --> architect : 6. Project initialized. Open arch.drawio in draw.io.

@enduml
